<link href="adcp.css" rel="stylesheet"><entry><xh5> ride a white horse • ride the white horse</xh5><p> <i>ride a white horse—</i>ride a horse of white color: The man who brought the buffalo went to them on horseback, <u>riding a white horse</u>.</p><p> <i>ride the white horse</i>—(sl., euph.) have one’s menstrual period: She’s <u>riding the white horse</u>. That’s why she’s a little cranky.</p> </entry>
